{"tid":378530,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"減緊肥既同路人不如分享下你地既餐單","createTime":"2017-08-28T14:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T04:30:19.000Z","uid":125218,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0fbedf97ef4a58bdbf3892e9bd9d37e055f32b","tid":378530,"uid":125218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:29:28.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早餐：想食得飽肚啲但唔知點健康地食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n午餐：帶飯 (菜：肉：主食 = 2 : 2 : 1) 清淡為主<br />\n晚餐：淨食餸，戒澱粉，食五分飽<br />\n運動：因為想減脂先，係咪應該做完無氧再落街跑30mins?求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c9ec6aa273394a2517c35c53cce26241eb4a3b","tid":378530,"uid":54411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/223322_08aa79cda21e7cf5759d3fa9a49c35dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F223322_08aa79cda21e7cf5759d3fa9a49c35dc.jpg&h=e0f17935&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/223322_87c5c9fbbce420b444d52d3fbdf87623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F223322_87c5c9fbbce420b444d52d3fbdf87623.jpg&h=079d7417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重點多菜 多瘦肉 食粗糧（糙米/番薯/栗米等）"},{"pid":"a15f6ece67d6bfe3e1f84d89547f7c8adf61f35d","tid":378530,"uid":10330,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:53:00.000Z","msg":"早餐 麥包蛋三文治<br />\n中午 正常<br />\n晚餐 唔食<br />\n維持一日食2餐 冇規律做運動 <br />\n睇心情去快行 去跳舞<br />\n2個月到瘦咗3kg"},{"pid":"0a8d6bbba63dc68387b1ff4588e26129400d7e98","tid":378530,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"早餐想飽肚 食兩-三隻蛋再加少少其他野食實飽"},{"pid":"3c842eb29dc3ace2d51a39b3342dd5fa5c48f4f7","tid":378530,"uid":60032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早餐 麥包蛋三文治<br />\n中午 正常<br />\n晚餐 唔食<br />\n維持一日食2餐 冇規律做運動 <br />\n睇心情去快行 去跳舞<br />\n2個月到瘦咗3kg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nintermittent fasting good ar"},{"pid":"b59fa3810ad63580b644998ba4cc47a76c8a6547","tid":378530,"uid":67606,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:05:19.000Z","msg":"早餐 m 記<br />\n午餐kfc<br />\n晚餐 出前一丁"},{"pid":"ae2a847bd42690539bd647597b61c3cf1799340e","tid":378530,"uid":125218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/223322_08aa79cda21e7cf5759d3fa9a49c35dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F223322_08aa79cda21e7cf5759d3fa9a49c35dc.jpg&h=e0f17935&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/223322_87c5c9fbbce420b444d52d3fbdf87623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F223322_87c5c9fbbce420b444d52d3fbdf87623.jpg&h=079d7417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重點多菜 多瘦肉 食粗糧（糙米/番薯/栗米等）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已買糙米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身都想買番薯同牛油果<br />\n但聽人講依兩樣都好似好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d54cf95588d0a398ac5972a82d8f617bdfc87f6","tid":378530,"uid":125218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早餐 麥包蛋三文治<br />\n中午 正常<br />\n晚餐 唔食<br />\n維持一日食2餐 冇規律做運動 <br />\n睇心情去快行 去跳舞<br />\n2個月到瘦咗3kg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但你去到四五點會唔會覺得好肚餓<br />\n我本身都同你食差唔多份量<br />\n成日依個鐘數就肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f296483f31bce76f584ac3abd397c55f5f485a","tid":378530,"uid":90303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:11:06.000Z","msg":"早:正常<br />\n午:正常<br />\n晚: 兩隻烚蛋加雞胸 有時加水果<br />\n一星期跑兩次步 一個月減1.5公斤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n減得好慢"},{"pid":"51e9dda2f662d99390b4c3b476fdcb8b52d93d3a","tid":378530,"uid":113700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"三個月由82KG減到70KG<br />\n朝早 麥皮+香蕉<br />\n中午 雞胸飯<br />\n晚餐 雞胸、比目魚/三文魚、牛+飯、菜<br />\n正餐之間食水果<br />\n小食以有良好脂肪既無鹽果仁為主<br />\n每餐盡量少油少鹽，多食高蛋白質低脂食物<br />\n每星期最少五日帶氧運動+重訓<br />\n唔可以戒澱粉質，因為係人體動力來源，做運動必要"},{"pid":"2bbc120028d925dd6a42a17ca217d9c680d575d0","tid":378530,"uid":10330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早餐 麥包蛋三文治<br />\n中午 正常<br />\n晚餐 唔食<br />\n維持一日食2餐 冇規律做運動 <br />\n睇心情去快行 去跳舞<br />\n2個月到瘦咗3kg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但你去到四五點會唔會覺得好肚餓<br />\n我本身都同你食差唔多份量<br />\n成日依個鐘數就肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時會就會食菜<br />\n通常11點先會餓 就直接瞓教"},{"pid":"f4d085287020c421a056bd57da4469818b2f288d","tid":378530,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/223322_08aa79cda21e7cf5759d3fa9a49c35dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F223322_08aa79cda21e7cf5759d3fa9a49c35dc.jpg&h=e0f17935&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/223322_87c5c9fbbce420b444d52d3fbdf87623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F223322_87c5c9fbbce420b444d52d3fbdf87623.jpg&h=079d7417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重點多菜 多瘦肉 食粗糧（糙米/番薯/栗米等）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已買糙米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身都想買番薯同牛油果<br />\n但聽人講依兩樣都好似好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛油果 番薯都唔驚 放心食<br />\n唔過量就ok"},{"pid":"c8370b4404ac643d15aa55308bde3fec99f790d6","tid":378530,"uid":10330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早:正常<br />\n午:正常<br />\n晚: 兩隻烚蛋加雞胸 有時加水果<br />\n一星期跑兩次步 一個月減1.5公斤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n減得好慢</blockquote><br />\n一個星期瘦 半磅 先係正常<br />\n瘦太快 對身體唔係咁好"},{"pid":"667fe82406c7bac5b38f596364a395cfb9c1e378","tid":378530,"uid":116665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:22:19.000Z","msg":"食野之前飲3杯水 食完再飲一杯 淨係食半碗飯加小小送飽晒<br />\n不過係咁去廁所<br />\n呢排戒晒零食 逼自己食少d 肉<br />\n我每日番工最少行13000步 但放假真係唔想郁<br />\n希望可以快d 瘦啦"},{"pid":"97e12225f2802b86f484592b9c0322c596ddcba4","tid":378530,"uid":20696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:36:02.000Z","msg":"早餐：麥皮+烚蛋1或者2隻，淨係食蛋白<br />\n有時係麥皮加1隻蕉<br />\n午餐：烚生菜+白魚蛋+烏冬<br />\n有時喺街/無時間會食7仔隻日式照燒雞青瓜三文治<br />\n如果餓嘅話下午會食1隻蕉/10粒車厘茄咁<br />\n晚餐：兩款菜+蒸魚+半碗飯（有時屋企人會手多加兩舊雞肉口痕會食埋，每次食完都後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飯後飲杯綠茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實覺得自己算食得多野減得好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過都打算長期作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> keep得住唔肥然後keep住有瘦已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過覺得自己晚餐真係食好多，但驚唔飽肚餓食宵夜仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經盡量食多啲菜塞飽自己，之後先食魚再食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1c958cdfea065396e3fa0c7096d3c907315ef0","tid":378530,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"每日只食三條soyjoy"},{"pid":"6eb949484b73d2026cd93c043237916469b5b749","tid":378530,"uid":116665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早餐：麥皮+烚蛋1或者2隻，淨係食蛋白<br />\n有時係麥皮加1隻蕉<br />\n午餐：烚生菜+白魚蛋+烏冬<br />\n有時喺街/無時間會食7仔隻日式照燒雞青瓜三文治<br />\n如果餓嘅話下午會食1隻蕉/10粒車厘茄咁<br />\n晚餐：兩款菜+蒸魚+半碗飯（有時屋企人會手多加兩舊雞肉口痕會食埋，每次食完都後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飯後飲杯綠茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實覺得自己算食得多野減得好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過都打算長期作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> keep得住唔肥然後keep住有瘦已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過覺得自己晚餐真係食好多，但驚唔飽肚餓食宵夜仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經盡量食多啲菜塞飽自己，之後先食魚再食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晚餐屋企人咁比心機煮 我都會食多dd <br />\n今晚先食左番茄洋蔥豬扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5541c3aabfef0a5ceb9a3a928e9e2fbc19dde8e","tid":378530,"uid":74315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:52:26.000Z","msg":"本人本身非常大食 減肥都係一定要食得飽<br />\n如果唔係堅持唔到<br />\n所以主要食既野主要係 少脂肪 少糖<br />\n<br />\n早餐： 自製三文治（麥包，青瓜/蕃茄，水浸吞拿魚/烚雞胸，蛋白）+香蕉一隻+脫脂希臘乳酪with新鮮藍莓<br />\n<br />\n午餐： 照常食但一定簡少油少糖 唔食肥肉 唔飲甜飲凍飲 make sure會有澱粉質同肉類/蛋白質<br />\n<br />\n下午茶：水果一至兩款（奇異果兩粒/雪梨/火龍果）<br />\n<br />\n晚餐：蔬菜為主 會食少少瘦肉 好肚餓會食幾匙飯（盡量糙米紅米溝白米）<br />\n<br />\n宵夜：盡戒 真係頂唔順可食生果/烚蛋白/青瓜<br />\n<br />\n平時戒零食<br />\n<br />\n一星期跑兩次 每次45分鐘 少少weight training<br />\n<br />\n咁樣持續左4個半月了 由58kg減到53.3kg而家 冇捱過餓 個身肌肉線條都好左好多"},{"pid":"c44411ecf529326d006fe407f666a4687a7c7edc","tid":378530,"uid":74315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/223322_08aa79cda21e7cf5759d3fa9a49c35dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F223322_08aa79cda21e7cf5759d3fa9a49c35dc.jpg&h=e0f17935&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/223322_87c5c9fbbce420b444d52d3fbdf87623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F223322_87c5c9fbbce420b444d52d3fbdf87623.jpg&h=079d7417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重點多菜 多瘦肉 食粗糧（糙米/番薯/栗米等）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已買糙米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身都想買番薯同牛油果<br />\n但聽人講依兩樣都好似好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛油果真係唔好 成舊脂肪黎<br />\n雖然係好脂肪但都會肥架"},{"pid":"b77a25ed39137d12ac5dce04f4f2aa9ca515c036","tid":378530,"uid":125218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早:正常<br />\n午:正常<br />\n晚: 兩隻烚蛋加雞胸 有時加水果<br />\n一星期跑兩次步 一個月減1.5公斤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n減得好慢</blockquote><br />\n一個星期瘦 半磅 先係正常<br />\n瘦太快 對身體唔係咁好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n瘦太快 減左嗰啲都係肌肉黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b8c732a5f1eb8bbd9be4676fb0022929077cfb","tid":378530,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/115004_b79608c4c189969b590aaf8c53333be2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F115004_b79608c4c189969b590aaf8c53333be2.jpg&h=75e00e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2a5589a9e57432f8418093dc8afe095588f327","tid":378530,"uid":125218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:57:36.000Z","msg":"參考完樓上巴絲啲餐單決定咁食 點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早餐：三文治/蕃薯/麥皮+山藥薏仁粉溝無糖豆漿<br />\n午餐：帶飯<br />\n下午茶：食無調味nuts/生果 (一個手掌份量）<br />\n晚餐：烚蛋+食餸唔食飯，多菜少肉，清淡為主<br />\n運動：一星期4-5日跑步，跑步前先做無氧運動，（腿部/臀部/核心三選二）"},{"pid":"c99426975eef6b594d8fc7398df2d7465d947d19","tid":378530,"uid":125218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:58:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/115004_b79608c4c189969b590aaf8c53333be2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F115004_b79608c4c189969b590aaf8c53333be2.jpg&h=75e00e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經引誘唔到我架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3c0b02232ca782a9d7d37bdc3833c3655618eb","tid":378530,"uid":14190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:14:07.000Z","msg":"早餐：公仔麵或者唔食<br />\n午餐:煎餃 /炒飯/正常飯餸<br />\n晚餐:正常飯餸"},{"pid":"9301baf1c2ce93ee81d508071ace334d8fc4c24f","tid":378530,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:32:09.000Z","msg":"雞/焗魚柳/鴨胸/豬/牛 走肥走皮<br />\n<br />\n飯/意+菜 走汁<br />\n<br />\n檸汁/鹽/胡椒 調味"}]}